	<h2><font color="006600">Loose Ends</font></h2><a href="http://www.go-mono.com/">Mono</a>.&nbsp; The Open-Source implementation of the .NET Development Framework.&nbsp; Right now they have a C# compiler, a CLR implementation, and a set of class libraries.&nbsp; These are in a variety of stages, but there is interesting movement.&nbsp; This should not be confused with Roter, which is the Shared-Source implementation supported by Microsoft and not satisfying the Open-Source Definition.<br>
