	<a name="84930883">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://coworking.com/">CoWorking</a>.&nbsp; There is reference to Coworking Continued and I don't understand that subtlety.&nbsp; Maybe it is an inside joke.&nbsp; This is one of the sites being promoted by Gerrit, who sent out some notices about sharing and win-win approaches.<br>
