	<h2>Trust and Security</h2>This is an on-going theme in my studies and writing.<h3>Operating-system security exposures</h3><a href="http://www.newsfactor.com/perl/printer/19996/">Study: Linux' Security Problems Outstrip Microsoft's</a>.&nbsp; The math quoted in here doesn't seem to stack up based on the Microsoft Security Alerts that I receive.&nbsp; At the same time, this is plausible and was predicted by security experts.&nbsp; I can't wait to see how this shows up on Slashdot.<br>
